text: The William I. Cole House is located in Fond du Lac, Wisconsin. ==History== William I. Cole was a bank vice president. The house was added to the State Register of Historic Places in 2001 and to the National Register of Historic Places the following year. ==References== Category:Houses on the National Register of Historic Places in Wisconsin Category:National Register of Historic Places in Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin Category:Houses in Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin Category:Italianate architecture in Wisconsin Category:Houses completed in 1857
title: William I. Cole House
